 課程用書：

和聲學：
Aldwell, Edward and 
					Carl Schachter. Harmony and Voice Leading. Second 
					Edition. New York: Harcourt Brace Jovanovich, 1989.
對位法：
Jeppesen, Knud. 
					Counterpoint. Englewood Cliffs: Prentice Hall, Inc., 1939.





Kennan, 
								Kent. Counterpoint Based on 
								Eighteenth-Century Practice, 4th 
								ed. New Jersey: Prentice-Hall, 1999.
Salzer, 
								Felix, and Carl Schachter. Counterpoint 
								in Composition. New York: McGraw-Hill Book 
								Company, 1969. 


樂曲分析：

Cadwallader, Allen and David Gagné. Analysis 
					of Tonal Music: A Schenkerian Approach. 
					New York: Oxford University Press, 1998.


					Cook, Nicholas. A Guide to Musical Analysis. New York: G. 
					Braziller, 1987.

Green, Douglass M. 
					Form in Tonal Music: An Introduction to Analysis. 2nd 
					ed. New York: Holt, Rinehart and Winston, 1979. 



Rosen, Charles. The Romantic Generation. 
					Massachusetts: Harvard University Press, 1995.

					作曲技巧探討：

Schwarts, Elliot and 
					Daniel Godfrey. Music Since 1945: Issues, Materials, and 
					Literature. New York: Schirmer Books, 1993.

Stefan, Kostka. 
					Materials and Techniques of Twentieth-Century Music. New 
					Jersey: Prentice Hall, 1990.

					樂器學、配器法、管弦樂法：

Adler, Samuel. The 
					Study of Orchestration, 2nd ed. New York: W. W. 
					Norton, 1989.


					Blatter, Alfred. Instrumentation and Orchestration. 
					New York: Prentice Hall, 1997.

					數位音訊合成：

Miranda, Eduardo Reck. Computer Sound 
					Design – Synthesis Techniques and Programming. 2nd 
					ed. Massachusetts: Focal Press, 2002.


Roads, Curtis. The Computer Music Tutorial. 
					Ma.: Massachusetts Institute of Technology, 1996

					數位混音：

Lzhaki, Roey. Mixing 
					Audio – Concepts, Practice and Tools. MA: Focal Press, 2008.

Katz, Bob. 
					Mastering Audio – the Art and the Science. 2nd 
					Edition. MA: Focal Press, 2002.

					錄音工程：

Huber, David Miles. 
					Modern Recording Techniques, 6th Edition. Burlington, 
					MA: Focal Press, 2005.

Bartlett, Bruce. 
					Practical Recording Techniques. Indiana: Prentice Hall 
					Computer Publishing, 1992.
　
　







